25:05.789 --> 25:10.616
Meanwhile, we'd love to hear from you on social media or through our free Jerusalem channel mobile app.

25:11.057 --> 25:22.895
Please follow my articles at substat.com and all our videos at our Jerusalem channel YouTube platform as well as our website exploits.tv where you have the opportunities to support our work financially.

25:23.856 --> 25:30.226
Finally, we invite you to sign up for our weekly email alert called exploits based upon Daniel 1132

25:30.306 --> 25:36.273
declaring the people who know their God will be strong, not weak, and we're going to accomplish biblical exploits.

25:36.714 --> 25:40.258
That's the works of the Lord in the remaining time before His imminent return.

25:41.179 --> 25:46.526
Meanwhile, let's keep contending for the faith and praying prophetically for the peace of Jerusalem.

25:46.846 --> 25:49.830
I'm Christine Darg, Shalom and Maranatha.

25:53.074 --> 25:55.677
We're in a season to be giving and receiving gifts.

25:55.958 --> 25:59.442
I'm excited to announce a newly published book in paperback called

25:59.746 --> 26:05.672
50 Gifts of the Holy Spirit on Amazon, and it's available both in print and in ebook.

26:06.233 --> 26:11.278
The Holy Spirit offers far more than the nine commonly taught gifts of the Spirit.

26:11.298 --> 26:17.685
Scripture reveals a rich array of divine empowerment for everyday life, spiritual growth, and kingdom impact.

26:18.386 --> 26:29.458
In my newly revised second edition, I describe many ways in which the Holy Spirit equips the Church, unpacking truths on how God still speaks, heals, and guides today

26:29.602 --> 26:33.426
through his word, dreams, visions, and gifts of the Holy Spirit.

26:34.207 --> 26:44.177
In more than 100 pages, I explore at least 50 distinct spiritual gifts that I've discovered all in this Bible, ranging from prophecy to hospitality.

26:44.678 --> 26:52.045
And I attempt to explain why the body of Messiah needs every gift operational to prepare for the Lord's return.

26:52.786 --> 26:56.850
I also tackle the difference between gifts and the fruit of the Spirit,

26:57.218 --> 27:00.141
and why both are vital for our mature faith.

27:00.862 --> 27:10.192
I want to encourage you with such good news that the Holy Spirit distributes gifts way beyond our human limitations, family background, or natural skills.

27:10.953 --> 27:22.686
From administration to mercy, craftsmanship, and discerning of spirits, each expression of the Holy Spirit is a vital tool, freely given by generous God to build up the living church.

27:23.347 --> 27:26.450
The gifts of the Spirit has prepared for you

27:26.562 --> 27:29.827
are irrevocable and yours to walk in forever.

27:30.609 --> 27:38.782
Fifty gifts of the Holy Spirit should be available by time this broadcast is released, and it's a greatly expanded version of my first edition.

27:39.403 --> 27:48.137
I believe this book is vital to dealing with our times because Bible prophecy can be better understood if the gifts of the Spirit are alive and our lives.

27:48.698 --> 27:53.906
Gifting such as the discerning of spirits so vital in a world of increasing deception.

27:54.562 --> 27:59.649
The gifts of the Holy Spirit can be likened to all the various tools in a tool chest.

27:59.669 --> 28:05.137
When the Holy Spirit resides within us, all of his manifold gifts are potentially resident within us.

28:05.757 --> 28:11.005
A friend wrote to me that this book transformed his thinking and was a real blessing for himself and family.

28:11.966 --> 28:20.818
Wherever you are in the world, you can order 50 gifts of the Holy Spirit by searching for that title under the books by Christine Darg, available at Amazon.

